<header>
  <h1>PocketPages Board</h1>
  <p>게시판 서비스의 시작 화면입니다. 현재는 `boards` 컬렉션 목록만 단순하게 보여줍니다.</p>
</header>

<section class="grid">
  <article x-data="{ q: '' }">
    <header>
      <strong>Board List</strong>
    </header>

    <label>
      Search
      <input type="search" x-model="q" placeholder="Search board name or slug" />
    </label>

    <div id="board-list">
      <%- include('board-list.ejs', {
        boards: data.boards,
        error: data.error,
        selectedBoardSlug: '',
      }) %>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article x-data="{ open: false, name: '', slug: '' }">
    <header>
      <strong>Create Board</strong>
    </header>

    <button type="button" @click="open = !open" x-text="open ? 'Close' : 'New board'"></button>

    <form
      x-show="open"
      x-transition
      hx-post="/api/boards/create"
      hx-target="#board-create-feedback"
      hx-swap="innerHTML"
      hx-on::after-request="if(event.detail.successful){ this.reset(); open = false; }"
    >
      <label>
        Name
        <input type="text" name="name" x-model="name" placeholder="General Discussion" required />
      </label>

      <label>
        Slug
        <input type="text" name="slug" x-model="slug" placeholder="general-discussion" />
        <small x-show="name || slug">
          Preview:
          <span x-text="slug || name.toLowerCase().trim().replace(/[^a-z0-9]+/g, '-').replace(/^-|-$/g, '')"></span>
        </small>
      </label>

      <label>
        Description
        <textarea name="description" placeholder="Board description"></textarea>
      </label>

      <button type="submit">Create</button>
    </form>

    <div id="board-create-feedback"></div>
  </article>
</section>

<article>
  <header>
    <strong>Posts</strong>
    <p>보드를 선택하면 해당 게시글 목록을 HTMX로 불러옵니다.</p>
  </header>
  <%- include('post-panel.ejs', {
    selectedBoard: null,
    selectedBoardSlug: '',
    posts: [],
  }) %>
</article>
